text:
Question for whoever is the lead on recruiting:

What’s our standard point of contact for folks who may be interested in applying for jobs? Should I just send them to our careers page or do we want them to contact anyone in particular?
Asking here in preparation for the Code Oregon Lab event this Thursday.
Cool, so send them directly to you?
i’ll give you some of my cards if you’d like
Yes, that would be awesome. Thanks.
